                        "new birth provides the power to obey. Then the victory declaration: 'Everyone who has been "
                        "born of God overcomes (nika) the world. And this is the victory (nike) that has overcome "
                        "the world -- our faith' (5:4). The kosmos -- the organized human system under the evil "
